text: Sedina pratyeka um'matera madhye ami ekajana barnanakari damra karaba tadera bipakse tadera madhya theke'i ebam tadera bisaye apanake saksi sbarupa upasthapana karaba. Ami apanara prati grantha nayila karechi yeti emana ye ta pratyeka bastura suspasta barnana, hedayeta, rahamata ebam musalamanadera jan'ye susambada.
